<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="296" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,151,1544]" pageId="4" pageNumber="296">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,308,1484,1509]" pageId="4" pageNumber="296">Remarks</emphasis>
. Large body size, strongly contrasting colors, and the shape of male and female genitalia, aid in the recognition of this species.
</paragraph>
